  <brief_title>Blood Pressure Reduction Induced by CPAP in Sleep Apnea Patients at High Cardiovascular Risk : OPTISAS 2 Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Blood Pressure Reduction Induced by Continuous Positive Airway Pressure (CPAP) in Sleep Apnea Patients at High Cardiovascular Risk : A Randomized Controlled Trial Comparing Usual CPAP Care Versus a Multidisciplinary and Coordinated Follow-up Based on a Telemonitoring Web Platform</official_title>
